  The Model Context Protocol (MCP) implementation for the Universal Object Reference (UOR) Framework
  provides a standardized way for LLMs to access and manipulate UOR data. This implementation uses
  GitHub for data storage and version control, enabling a decentralized approach to UOR data management.
